							"top": 1424,
							"width": 224,
							"height": 104,
							"text": "Semantic Memory and Episodic Memory is being injected on the think() method instead of the class itself. That way the devs can reuse the MagickMind class even when they change the SemanticMemory and EpisodicMemory."
